Anyhow, back to the topic at hand, the sheer scale of the proposed ship was amazing! I think that we should have gone on to Rover/NERVA systems as a go-between while Orion would have been in full production and development. It’s a great book and if you want something  fun to read I highly recommend it.  <br>
